---
// src/pages/guides/prestige.astro
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="Prestige Guide" description="How to prestige in Bizarre Lineage. Requirements, steps, rewards, and tips for all 3 prestige levels." canonicalPath="/guides/prestige">
  <section class="section"><div class="container guide-content">
    <nav class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">← Home</a> <span class="sep">/</span> <span>Guides</span></nav>
    <h1>Bizarre Lineage Prestige Guide</h1>
    <p class="lead">Everything you need to know about the Prestige system. Up to 3 Prestige levels for permanent bonuses.</p>

    <div class="guide-nav">
      <a href="/guides/leveling">Leveling</a>
      <a href="/guides/prestige" class="active">Prestige</a>
      <a href="/guides/awakening">Awakening</a>
    </div>

    <h2>What Is Prestige?</h2>
    <p>Prestige resets your character level to 1 but grants permanent bonuses and additional Stand storage. You can prestige up to <strong>3 times</strong>, each requiring you to reach max level again.</p>

    <h2>Prestige Requirements</h2>
    <div class="req-grid">
      <div class="req-card"><span class="req-num">1</span><h3>Prestige 1</h3><ul><li>Level 50 (max)</li><li>$10,000 cash</li><li>+5 Prestige Points</li><li>+1 Stand Storage Slot</li></ul></div>
      <div class="req-card"><span class="req-num">2</span><h3>Prestige 2</h3><ul><li>Level 50 (again)</li><li>$25,000 cash</li><li>+5 Prestige Points</li><li>+1 Stand Storage Slot</li><li>Unlocks Spin Sub-Ability</li></ul></div>
      <div class="req-card"><span class="req-num">3</span><h3>Prestige 3 (Max)</h3><ul><li>Level 50 (again)</li><li>$50,000 cash</li><li>+5 Prestige Points</li><li>+1 Stand Storage Slot</li><li>Unlocks exclusive cosmetics</li></ul></div>
    </div>

    <h2>How to Prestige — Step by Step</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Reach <strong>max level (50)</strong> and accumulate the required cash amount</li>
      <li>Travel to <strong>TC Hospital (Bus Stop 10)</strong></li>
      <li>Find and interact with the <strong>Arch Mage NPC</strong></li>
      <li>Confirm the prestige — your level resets to 1, but you keep your Stand and Sub-Abilities</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>What You Keep vs. What Resets</h2>
    <div class="keep-table">
      <table>
        <thead><tr><th>✅ Keep</th><th>❌ Reset</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Current Stand</td><td>Character Level → 1</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Sub-Abilities</td><td>Stat Points (redistributable)</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Fighting Style</td><td>Cash spent on prestige</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Prestige Points</td><td>Quest progress</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="tip-box">
      <h3>💡 Pro Tip</h3>
      <p>After prestiging, leveling is faster because you already have a max-level Stand. Use your strong abilities to farm high-level areas from Level 1. Check our <a href="/guides/leveling">Leveling Guide</a> for the optimal route.</p>
    </div>
  </div></section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .guide-content { max-width: 780px; }
  .breadcrumb { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.82rem; color: #64748b; }
  .breadcrumb a { color: #7c3aed; text-decoration: none; } .sep { margin: 0 0.3rem; }
  h1 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: #fff; margin: 0 0 0.5rem; }
  .lead { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 1rem; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; }
  .guide-nav { display: flex; gap: 0.4rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; padding-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .guide-nav a { padding: 0.4rem 1rem; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500; color: #94a3b8; transition: all 0.2s; }
  .guide-nav a.active { background: rgba(124,58,237,0.12); color: #a855f7; }
  h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #e2e8f0; margin: 2rem 0 0.8rem; }
  p { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  p strong { color: #e2e8f0; }
  ol, ul { padding-left: 1.2rem; } li { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.88rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  li strong { color: #e2e8f0; } li a, p a { color: #a855f7; }
  .req-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1rem; }
  .req-card { background: var(--color-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 14px; padding: 1.2rem; position: relative; }
  .req-num { position: absolute; top: -8px; right: 12px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed, #a855f7); color: #fff; width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; }
  .req-card h3 { margin: 0 0 0.5rem; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #e2e8f0; }
  .req-card ul { padding-left: 1rem; margin: 0; }
  .req-card li { font-size: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
  .keep-table { overflow-x: auto; margin: 1rem 0; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.85rem; }
  th { text-align: left; padding: 0.6rem 0.8rem; color: #e2e8f0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); font-weight: 600; }
  td { padding: 0.6rem 0.8rem; color: #94a3b8; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(124,58,237,0.06); }
  .tip-box { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245,158,11,0.08), rgba(124,58,237,0.06)); border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.2); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.2rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
  .tip-box h3 { margin: 0 0 0.4rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #f59e0b; }
  .tip-box p { margin: 0; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #e2e8f0; }
  @media (max-width: 640px) { .req-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
